<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>عن يحيى بن عبد الله البَابَلُتِّي<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>والبيهقي في <span class="c1">"الخلافيات"</span> <span class="c2">(٥٠٨)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
